public final class OcamlBuildContext
extends Object
    OCaml build context

    OCaml has two build modes, "native" (ocamlopt) and "bytecode" (ocamlc), and that terminology is used throughout this file -- not to be confused with the "native" terminology used in com.facebook.buck.cxx.toolchain.nativelink.NativeLinkableInput.
